    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six with individual throttle bodies. This example features a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for precise torque distribution. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement. The rear subframe has been reinforced to ensure chassis longevity and torsional rigidity. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its mileage, the suspension geometry is dialed in with refreshed bushings and dampers, offering a visceral and communicative driving experience. A true enthusiast's specimen that balances raw performance with proven reliability.",
